data.description: Imagine the joy of returning to this wonderfully spacious and lovingly maintained home. Situated on a lovely lot surrounded by mature landscaping, this charming residence welcomes you with open arms. From the large front porch, step into the cozy Living Room, perfect for relaxing evenings, or gather with loved ones in the Dining Room. The Family Room has a cozy brick-front fireplace and access to the heated Sun Room. And let's not forget the spacious Kitchen, complete with oak cabinets, wood edge counters, and a convenient island - it's a chef's dream! Upstairs, the spacious Owner's Suite awaits an ensuite Bathroom and dual closets, while three additional Bedrooms and a hall bathroom offer plenty of space for everyone. The basement features a large Rec Room, and an unfinished utility area
